                </tp:treatment-sec>
                <tp:treatment-sec sec-type="Distribution">
                    <title>Distribution.</title>
                    <p>South Africa.</p>
                </tp:treatment-sec>
                <tp:treatment-sec sec-type="Etymology">
                    <title>Etymology.</title>
                    <p>From the preexisting name <italic><tp:taxon-name><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus">Poliocoris</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name></italic> and the prefix “Neo-” from the Greek “<italic>neos</italic>”, meaning new; gender masculine.</p>
